lead_paragraph: Marc Gasol had 26 points and 12 rebounds, and the Memphis Grizzlies finally put away the short-handed Philadelphia 76ers 96-91 on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Gasol Has 26 Points, 12 Boards to Lead Grizzlies Past Sixers
